_sText:
These are automated health generator.
the differences in size:
Large can fit on person to hide inside the device.
medium is the same size as the large height wise but shallower and cant fit people within the device.
small is a wall mounted (if you wish) and looks just like a regular health kit.

the health bots are all activated by pushing "E" on the Red cross button on the front.

if you wish to use this prefab, please rate this prefab and credit me (CM375508).
